#: ../../docs/training_manual/appendix/contribute.rst:313
msgid "Adding a sponsorship/authorship note"
msgstr "Dodavanje napomene o sponzorstvu/autorstvu"

#: ../../docs/training_manual/appendix/contribute.rst:315
msgid ""
"If you are writing a new module, lesson or section on behalf of a sponsor, "
"you must include a short sponsor message of their choice. This must notify "
"the reader of the name of the sponsor and must appear below the heading of "
"the module, lesson or section that they sponsored. However, it may not be an"
" advertisement for their company."
msgstr ""
"Ako pišete novi modul, lekciju ili odeljak u ime sponzora, morate uključiti "
"kratku sponzorsku poruku po njihovom izboru. Ona mora obavestiti čitaoca o "
"nazivu sponzora i mora se pojaviti ispod naslova modula, lekcije ili odeljka"
" koji su sponzorisali. Međutim, ne sme biti reklama za njihovu kompaniju."

#: ../../docs/training_manual/appendix/contribute.rst:321
msgid ""
"If you have volunteered to write a module, lesson or section in your own "
"capacity, and not on behalf of a sponsor, you may include an authorship note"
" below the heading of the module, lesson or section that you authored. This "
"must take the form ``This [module/lesson/section] contributed by [author "
"name].`` Do not add further text, contact details, etc. Such details are to "
"be added in the \"Contributors\" section of the Foreword, along with the "
"name(s) of the part(s) you added. If you only made enhancements, corrections"
" and/or additions, list yourself as an editor."
msgstr ""
"Ako ste se dobrovoljno prijavili da napišete modul, lekciju ili odeljak u "
"svoje ime, a ne u ime sponzora, možete uključiti napomenu o autorstvu ispod "
"naslova modula, lekcije ili odeljka koji ste napisali. Ona mora biti u "
"obliku ``This [module/lesson/section] contributed by [author name].`` Ne "
"dodajte dodatni tekst, kontakt podatke i sl. Takvi podaci dodaju se u "
"odeljak „Contributors“ u Predgovoru, zajedno sa nazivima delova koje ste "
"dodali. Ako ste napravili samo poboljšanja, ispravke i/ili dopune, navedite "
"se kao urednik."

#: ../../docs/training_manual/appendix/contribute.rst:331
msgid "Thank You!"
msgstr "Hvala vam!"

#: ../../docs/training_manual/appendix/contribute.rst:333
msgid ""
"Thank you for contributing to this project! By so doing, you are making QGIS"
" more accessible to users and adding value to the QGIS project as a whole."
msgstr ""
"Hvala vam što doprinosite ovom projektu! Time činite QGIS pristupačnijim "
"korisnicima i dodajete vrednost celom QGIS projektu."
